diting\">M\u00e1s inFORMACI\u00d3N<\/span><\/a><\/div><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-container uagb-block-7bf30896 alignfull uagb-is-root-container\"><div class=\"uagb-container-inner-blocks-wrap\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-container uagb-block-20cff6b0\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-image uagb-block-664c3898 wp-block-uagb-image--layout-default wp-block-uagb-image--effect-static wp-block-uagb-image--align-none\"><figure class=\"wp-block-uagb-image__figure\"><img decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https:\/\/edencampestre.com.mx\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/04\/Gemini_Generated_Image_svqj1ksvqj1ksvqj-e1777355820450-1024x1014.png ,https:\/\/edencampestre.com.mx\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/04\/Gemini_Generated_Image_svqj1ksvqj1ksvqj-e1777355820450.png 780w, https:\/\/edencampestre.com.mx\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/04\/Gemini_Generated_Image_svqj1ksvqj1ksvqj-e1777355820450.png 360w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 480px) 150px\" src=\"https:\/\/edencampestre.com.mx\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/04\/Gemini_Generated_Image_svqj1ksvqj1ksvqj-e1777355820450-1024x1014.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"uag-image-531\" width=\"1024\" height=\"554\" title=\"CERCANIA\" loading=\"lazy\" role=\"img\"\/><\/figure><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-container uagb-block-95107aaa\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-advanced-heading uagb-block-2b5f49af\"><h3 class=\"uagb-heading-text\">Ubicaci\u00f3n estrat\u00e9gica<\/h3><div class=\"uagb-separator\"><\/div><p class=\"uagb-desc-text\">Su inmejorable ubicaci\u00f3n te garantiza un traslado r\u00e1pido y sin el estr\u00e9s del tr\u00e1fico hacia Canc\u00fan y Playa del Carmen. Adem\u00e1s, tendr\u00e1s la espectacular Ruta de los Cenotes pr\u00e1cticamente en tu patio trasero, convirtiendo cada d\u00eda en una oportunidad para escapar de la rutina y disfrutar del Caribe Mexicano a tu propio ritmo.<\/p><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-container uagb-block-1f082917 alignfull uagb-is-root-container\"><div class=\"uagb-container-inner-blocks-wrap\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-container uagb-block-cb51aae9\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-advanced-heading uagb-block-1ae7d129\"><h3 class=\"uagb-heading-text\">Adquirir tu patrimonio nunca fue tan f\u00e1cil<\/h3><div class=\"uagb-separator\"><\/div><p class=\"uagb-desc-text\">Pensando en tu futuro, hemos dise\u00f1ado un esquema de inversi\u00f3n inigualable: <br>Aparta tu terreno con solo el 10% de enganche y aprovecha nuestro financiamiento directo de hasta 60 meses sin intereses, con mensualidades m\u00ednimas desde  $3,000 MXN.<\/p><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-container uagb-block-171fdc51\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-image uagb-block-412be4db wp-block-uagb-image--layout-default wp-block-uagb-image--effect-static wp-block-uagb-image--align-none\"><figure class=\"wp-block-uagb-image__figure\"><img decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https:\/\/edencampestre.com.mx\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/04\/Picsart_26-04-25_22-37-10-693.jpg-1.jpeg ,https:\/\/edencampestre.com.mx\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/04\/Picsart_26-04-25_22-37-10-693.jpg-1.jpeg 780w, https:\/\/edencampestre.com.mx\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/04\/Picsart_26-04-25_22-37-10-693.jpg-1.jpeg 360w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 480px) 150px\" src=\"https:\/\/edencampestre.com.mx\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/04\/Picsart_26-04-25_22-37-10-693.jpg-1.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"uag-image-469\" width=\"1024\" height=\"554\" title=\"LOTES\" loading=\"lazy\" role=\"img\"\/><\/figure><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-container uagb-block-9d11d69e alignfull uagb-is-root-container\"><div class=\"uagb-container-inner-blocks-wrap\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-container uagb-block-3e1c392d\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-image uagb-block-f491a36b wp-block-uagb-image--layout-default wp-block-uagb-image--effect-static wp-block-uagb-image--align-none\"><figure class=\"wp-block-uagb-image__figure\"><img decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https:\/\/edencampestre.com.mx\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/04\/edenS-Model_page-0001-edited-1.jpg ,https:\/\/edencampestre.com.mx\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/04\/edenS-Model_page-0001-edited-1.jpg 780w, https:\/\/edencampestre.com.mx\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/04\/edenS-Model_page-0001-edited-1.jpg 360w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 480px) 150px\" src=\"https:\/\/edencampestre.com.mx\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/04\/edenS-Model_page-0001-edited-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"uag-image-567\" width=\"1024\" height=\"554\" title=\"LOTIFICACION\" loading=\"lazy\" role=\"img\"\/><\/figure><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-container uagb-block-0a5058f9\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-advanced-heading uagb-block-07a64d12\"><h3 class=\"uagb-heading-text\">Tu pedazo de para\u00edso y tranquilidad<\/h3><div class=\"uagb-separator\"><\/div><p class=\"uagb-desc-text\">Contamos con espaciosos terrenos de 40&#215;20 y 40&#215;40 metros, listos para adaptarse a tus necesidades.<\/p><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div id=\"AMENIDADES\" class=\"wp-block-uagb-container uagb-block-1f516663 alignfull uagb-is-root-container\"><div class=\"uagb-container-inner-blocks-wrap\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-advanced-heading uagb-block-be7dffa1\"><h3 class=\"uagb-heading-text\">Amenidades Exclusivas<\/h3><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-advanced-heading uagb-block-502b74a2\"><h1 class=\"uagb-heading-text\">Todo lo que necesitas para una vida en total equilibrio<\/h1><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-container uagb-layout-grid uagb-block-2ae5bed9 alignfull uagb-is-root-container\"><div class=\"uagb-container-inner-blocks-wrap\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-container uagb-block-9b7bb285\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-image uagb-block-8a685c5d wp-block-uagb-image--layout-default wp-block-uagb-image--effect-static wp-block-uagb-image--align-none\"><figure class=\"wp-block-uagb-image__figure\"><img decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"http